{"tid":1198613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊行隊伍點點「手提燭光」，對上次係幾時？細心一諗","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T09:38:32.000Z","uid":258193,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49a994cd4220d3c7e86a24bc1b58d68655fcd6ba","tid":1198613,"uid":258193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"昨天晚上遊行隊伍亮起手提電話，就像點點燭光。<br />\n印象中這是個似曾相識畫面，對上一次是何時？<br />\n原來上次是2017年選特首，曾俊華好多粉絲民望很高，怎至令大批市民為佢點起「手提燭光」。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/489875/org/f07022be4fe0234bd4b5435ac13833dd.jpg/QqzPVxatcrbGEgB5BeyYrb1fAiv3DxeEU0l641NJeuM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F489875%2Forg%2Ff07022be4fe0234bd4b5435ac13833dd.jpg%2FQqzPVxatcrbGEgB5BeyYrb1fAiv3DxeEU0l641NJeuM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=24635066&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後，即刻check入薯片叔叔的專頁，發現5月31日後便沒有回應和更新。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cBcKk05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBcKk05.png&h=65f070cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qqCRLsN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqqCRLsN.png&h=2eb182f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSEE! SEE!SEE! <br />\n佢落敗當日仲叫大家千萬不要放棄香港，然後佢呢次有無同市民同行過？無！ <br />\n利申：無支持過佢<br />\n<br />\n只係想講<br />\n無論當選的是某娥還是誰，中央事在必行，只是需要一個快恨準的人執行出來。"},{"pid":"1811d348dd7b9b788c52a4d92acd10d5a963ed62","tid":1198613,"uid":87930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:38:32.000Z","msg":"如果星期三又係咁9fing fing又有乜用？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1198514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1198514</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n依個方法行唔行得通？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />盡力諗"}]}